title: Miccosukee Championship
text:
The Miccosukee Championship was a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Web.com%20Tour">Web.com Tour</a> from 2003 to 2012. It was played at the Miccosukee Golf & Country Club in <a href="Miami%2C%20Florida">Miami, Florida</a>, U.S.
The 2012 purse was $600,000, with $108,000 going to the winner.
Winners.
Bolded golfers graduated to the PGA Tour via the final Web.com Tour money list.
